156
00:14:49,879 --> 00:14:51,360
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, Bog me oslobodio od cigarete.

157
00:14:51,360 --> 00:14:52,240
[SPEAKER_01] A kamo li što drugo?

158
00:14:52,240 --> 00:14:53,440
