549
00:25:29,200 --> 00:25:31,200
[SPEAKER_01] znači otac slaži koliko se bori

550
00:25:31,200 --> 00:25:33,339
[SPEAKER_01] sa našim duhom svijetim,

551
00:25:33,339 --> 00:25:34,440
[SPEAKER_01] duhom životvorcem,

552
00:25:34,440 --> 00:25:35,400
[SPEAKER_01] duhom braniteljem,

553
00:25:35,400 --> 00:25:36,440
[SPEAKER_01] duhom tješiteljem,

554
00:25:36,440 --> 00:25:38,079
[SPEAKER_01] duhom Božem istine,

555
00:25:38,079 --> 00:25:40,779
[SPEAKER_01] da se tamo ne raskrinka,

556
00:25:40,779 --> 00:25:42,099
[SPEAKER_01] baš je bila ta borba,

557
00:25:42,099 --> 00:25:43,579
[SPEAKER_01] da se tamo ne raskrinka,

558
00:25:43,579 --> 00:25:44,559
[SPEAKER_01] a u konočnici,

559
00:25:44,559 --> 00:25:46,500
[SPEAKER_01] to je najveća zamka Sotone,

560
00:25:46,500 --> 00:25:48,400
[SPEAKER_01] uvjeriti čovjeka,

561
00:25:48,400 --> 00:25:49,359
[SPEAKER_01] palog čovjeka,

562
00:25:49,359 --> 00:25:50,299
[SPEAKER_01] čovjeka slabog,

563
00:25:50,299 --> 00:25:51,519
[SPEAKER_01] da on ne postoji,

564
00:25:51,519 --> 00:25:53,180
[SPEAKER_01] da on tamo neki mit,

565
00:25:53,180 --> 00:25:54,119
[SPEAKER_01] nešto iz filma,

566
00:25:54,119 --> 00:25:55,319
[SPEAKER_01] nešto iz priča,

567
00:25:55,319 --> 00:25:56,339
[SPEAKER_01] davnina i tako,

568
00:25:56,339 --> 00:25:57,220
[SPEAKER_01] a to nije istina,

569
00:25:57,779 --> 00:25:59,779
[SPEAKER_01] duhovni svijet i takako postoji,

570
00:25:59,779 --> 00:26:01,140
[SPEAKER_01] i takako je stvaran,

571
00:26:01,140 --> 00:26:04,259
[SPEAKER_01] i takako svaki dan je borba za naše duše.

572
00:26:04,259 --> 00:26:09,380
[SPEAKER_00] U kojim trenucima se ti najviše uvjerila u to da je duhovni svijet stvaran?

573
00:26:10,660 --> 00:26:11,980
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam došla na tabor.

574
00:26:11,980 --> 00:26:13,660
[SPEAKER_01] Ali prije toga,

575
00:26:13,660 --> 00:26:15,180
[SPEAKER_01] kada sam bila kod Ante,

576
00:26:15,180 --> 00:26:17,859
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam ga nazvala,

577
00:26:17,859 --> 00:26:19,640
[SPEAKER_01] dođe pa meni u tu diskoteku,

578
00:26:19,640 --> 00:26:20,460
[SPEAKER_01] koju je došao,

579
00:26:20,460 --> 00:26:21,859
[SPEAKER_01] dobijem je k sebi doma,

580
00:26:21,859 --> 00:26:24,019
[SPEAKER_01] i gdje on već bi u sakramentima,

581
00:26:24,019 --> 00:26:24,940
[SPEAKER_01] či bi ispovjeđen,

582
00:26:24,940 --> 00:26:26,640
[SPEAKER_01] blagovaju tijelo Kristovo,

583
00:26:26,640 --> 00:26:27,619
[SPEAKER_01] kuhao i juhu,

584
00:26:27,619 --> 00:26:28,640
[SPEAKER_01] slušao duhovne pjesme,

585
00:26:28,640 --> 00:26:29,619
[SPEAKER_01] ko pjeva dvostrko,

586
00:26:29,619 --> 00:26:30,079
[SPEAKER_01] moli,

587
00:26:30,259 --> 00:26:34,859
[SPEAKER_01] i sve je to poticalo da se probude ti zlodusi u meni,

588
00:26:34,859 --> 00:26:36,099
[SPEAKER_01] gdje sam imala manifestacije,

589
00:26:36,099 --> 00:26:37,359
[SPEAKER_01] on je to snimao i se bojao,

590
00:26:37,359 --> 00:26:38,960
[SPEAKER_01] da se meni nešto ne dogodi.

591
00:26:38,960 --> 00:26:40,099
[SPEAKER_01] Drugi je mi pokazao,

592
00:26:40,099 --> 00:26:42,579
[SPEAKER_01] zavljaj pat razjezdana na tabor i poslužitelja,

593
00:26:42,579 --> 00:26:43,400
[SPEAKER_01] i sve,

594
00:26:43,400 --> 00:26:47,200
[SPEAKER_01] i tada sam shvatila da je jedna veća sila upravlja sa mnom.

595
00:26:47,200 --> 00:26:47,759
[SPEAKER_01] Iako,

596
00:26:47,759 --> 00:26:50,180
[SPEAKER_01] već prije kad sam ja ulazila u te grehe,

597
00:26:50,180 --> 00:26:50,759
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek sam imala,

598
00:26:50,759 --> 00:26:52,519
[SPEAKER_01] nekad dva glasa sam čula,

599
00:26:52,519 --> 00:26:53,680
[SPEAKER_01] jedan dobro i nemoj nič tu.

600
00:26:53,680 --> 00:26:55,740
[SPEAKER_01] Došla na sam vidjela neku sliku,

601
00:26:55,740 --> 00:26:57,180
[SPEAKER_01] dogodit će se to, to, to, to,

602
00:26:57,180 --> 00:27:00,140
[SPEAKER_01] i drugu silu koja me doslovno vukla,

603
00:27:00,140 --> 00:27:01,779
[SPEAKER_01] bacala u to blato,

604
00:27:01,779 --> 00:27:03,240
[SPEAKER_01] i onda iznad mene smijela.

605
00:27:03,240 --> 00:27:05,680
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, znao mi se dosta puta dogodi

606
00:27:05,680 --> 00:27:07,160
[SPEAKER_01] da sam se našla negdje,

607
00:27:07,160 --> 00:27:09,700
[SPEAKER_01] gdje pobudila sam se,

608
00:27:09,700 --> 00:27:11,359
[SPEAKER_01] evo, u nekoj hotelskoj sobi,

609
00:27:11,359 --> 00:27:12,380
[SPEAKER_01] gdje sam isto pisala,

610
00:27:12,380 --> 00:27:14,680
[SPEAKER_01] gdje sam, evo, bila na podu,

611
00:27:14,680 --> 00:27:16,759
[SPEAKER_01] niko nije bio kraj mene sama,

612
00:27:16,759 --> 00:27:17,740
[SPEAKER_01] omamljena,

613
00:27:17,740 --> 00:27:19,859
[SPEAKER_01] nisam znala uopće što se dogodilo s menom,

614
00:27:19,859 --> 00:27:21,799
[SPEAKER_01] tko se to je iživljavao nad menom,

615
00:27:21,799 --> 00:27:23,799
[SPEAKER_01] a samo sam jedno htjela doći doma,

616
00:27:23,799 --> 00:27:24,380
[SPEAKER_01] doći doma,

617
00:27:24,380 --> 00:27:26,859
[SPEAKER_01] staviti se po tu moju dekicu,

618
00:27:27,180 --> 00:27:28,799
[SPEAKER_01] skloniti se po tu moju dekicu

619
00:27:28,799 --> 00:27:30,680
[SPEAKER_01] i jednostavno da se obranim,

620
00:27:30,680 --> 00:27:33,220
[SPEAKER_01] da stavim neki štica tom svojom dekicom

621
00:27:33,220 --> 00:27:34,160
[SPEAKER_01] na sebe,

622
00:27:34,160 --> 00:27:36,339
[SPEAKER_01] ali onda kad dođeš na tabor

623
00:27:36,339 --> 00:27:39,539
[SPEAKER_01] i onda kad zaplovioš u tu dubine,

624
00:27:39,539 --> 00:27:41,559
[SPEAKER_01] dubine s gospodinom,

625
00:27:41,559 --> 00:27:42,880
[SPEAKER_01] dubine duhovnog svijeta,

626
00:27:42,880 --> 00:27:44,940
[SPEAKER_01] onda počinješ biti cjestan,

627
00:27:44,940 --> 00:27:47,359
[SPEAKER_01] ubiti kome si to sve služio

628
00:27:47,359 --> 00:27:49,680
[SPEAKER_01] u ovom životu, svijetu, tijelu, džavlu

629
00:27:49,680 --> 00:27:52,440
[SPEAKER_01] i u konačnici ko je tvoj jedini nepratelj,

630
00:27:52,440 --> 00:27:53,259
[SPEAKER_01] a to je satona,

631
00:27:53,259 --> 00:27:56,799
[SPEAKER_01] to nije čovjek ko je i slap, i grešan, i ranjen, i zerugljen.

632
00:27:57,180 --> 00:27:58,259
[SPEAKER_01] Ja znam s kojim imam borbu,

633
00:27:58,259 --> 00:28:00,480
[SPEAKER_01] znači nemam borbu sa niti ljudima,

634
00:28:00,480 --> 00:28:02,480
[SPEAKER_01] niti Hrvatima, niti Njemcima,

635
00:28:02,480 --> 00:28:05,180
[SPEAKER_01] niti Englezima, niti onom...

636
00:28:05,180 --> 00:28:06,880
[SPEAKER_01] nacijom.

637
00:28:06,880 --> 00:28:09,440
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nemam niti ras, znači ja se ne borim s čovjekom.

638
00:28:09,440 --> 00:28:10,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ja znam

639
00:28:10,119 --> 00:28:13,180
[SPEAKER_01] čija je moja borba, protiv koga se borim,

640
00:28:13,180 --> 00:28:14,519
[SPEAKER_01] ali Bogu hvala,

641
00:28:14,519 --> 00:28:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bog je jači od svakog zlajka,

642
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:18,059
[SPEAKER_01] kao što kaže sveti Mihajl,

643
00:28:18,059 --> 00:28:19,299
[SPEAKER_01] nitko kao Bok,

644
00:28:19,299 --> 00:28:20,700
[SPEAKER_01] i tko je s Bogom,

645
00:28:20,700 --> 00:28:24,339
[SPEAKER_01] Bok je s njim i Bok je istina koja pobjeđa uvijek.

646
00:28:24,339 --> 00:28:26,460
[SPEAKER_01] Nekad možda nije naše vreme,

647
00:28:26,460 --> 00:28:29,619
[SPEAKER_01] kad bi mi htjeli nešto da On prevede kraju,

648
00:28:29,619 --> 00:28:32,559
[SPEAKER_01] ili negdje da njegova desnica pobjedi,

649
00:28:32,559 --> 00:28:34,819
[SPEAKER_01] ali Bogu hvala strpljivost,

650
00:28:34,819 --> 00:28:36,940
[SPEAKER_01] strpljivost majka svih ostalih kreposti.

651
00:28:37,940 --> 00:28:38,500
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

652
00:28:38,500 --> 00:28:40,559
[SPEAKER_00] A što ti misliš,

653
00:28:40,559 --> 00:28:43,079
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno kako vidiš,

654
00:28:43,079 --> 00:28:50,660
[SPEAKER_00] kroz što je se po tebi najviše u tebe uvlačio taj zloduh

655
00:28:50,660 --> 00:28:52,160
[SPEAKER_00] koji te na kraju toliko zaposljio,

656
00:28:52,160 --> 00:28:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] da si ti zapravo godinama išla

657
00:28:54,000 --> 00:28:58,140
[SPEAKER_00] idući, odnosno na Euharistiju,

658
00:28:58,140 --> 00:28:59,140
[SPEAKER_00] da življavala te manifestacije,

659
00:28:59,140 --> 00:29:02,039
[SPEAKER_00] na kraju išla čak i koliko mjeseci.

660
00:29:02,039 --> 00:29:04,359
[SPEAKER_00] 11 mjeseci na egzorcizam.

661
00:29:04,359 --> 00:29:06,140
[SPEAKER_00] Znači to je bilo jedno zaposljednuće

662
00:29:06,839 --> 00:29:08,339
[SPEAKER_00] na jednoj visokoj razini,

663
00:29:08,339 --> 00:29:12,400
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno čvrsto te se dohvatilo.

664
00:29:12,400 --> 00:29:13,059
[SPEAKER_00] Što ti misliš?

665
00:29:13,059 --> 00:29:15,660
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nije to moglo možda zbog, ne znam,

666
00:29:15,660 --> 00:29:17,039
[SPEAKER_00] krivog društva ili je,

667
00:29:17,039 --> 00:29:21,539
[SPEAKER_00] ili je zbog možda odlazaka kod vidovnjakinje?

668
00:29:21,539 --> 00:29:22,059
[SPEAKER_00] Što misliš?

669
00:29:22,059 --> 00:29:23,359
[SPEAKER_00] Ili je to skup svega?

670
00:29:23,359 --> 00:29:26,279
[SPEAKER_00] Kako si došla do toga tako mlada?

671
00:29:26,279 --> 00:29:27,180
[SPEAKER_00] Pa mlada.

672
00:29:27,180 --> 00:29:31,440
[SPEAKER_01] Prvi greh koji se otisnio u mene je bio taj greh zlostavljena.

673
00:29:31,440 --> 00:29:33,740
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam bila seksualno zlostavljena

674
00:29:33,740 --> 00:29:36,400
[SPEAKER_01] što sam u jednom dijelom knjigu makla iz knjige.

675
00:29:36,599 --> 00:29:39,180
[SPEAKER_01] nisam htjela taj dio detaljirati o toj osobi.

676
00:29:39,180 --> 00:29:41,220
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam toj osobi oprostila

677
00:29:41,220 --> 00:29:43,380
[SPEAKER_01] i molim se za tu osobu

678
00:29:43,380 --> 00:29:46,039
[SPEAKER_01] i zaista moje srce je u miru prema toj osobi.

679
00:29:46,039 --> 00:29:47,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ima svakoj osobi

680
00:29:47,960 --> 00:29:49,799
[SPEAKER_01] koja je išta očinila

681
00:29:49,799 --> 00:29:51,779
[SPEAKER_01] prema meni, prema moj srcu,

682
00:29:51,779 --> 00:29:52,720
[SPEAKER_01] prema mome tijelu.

683
00:29:52,720 --> 00:29:55,980
[SPEAKER_01] jer znam, moj Isus je oprostio meni

684
00:29:55,980 --> 00:29:57,660
[SPEAKER_01] i kako ja da ne prostim onima

685
00:29:57,660 --> 00:29:59,420
[SPEAKER_01] koji ga ne poznaju,

686
00:29:59,420 --> 00:30:00,839
[SPEAKER_01] koji ga još nisu poznali,

687
00:30:00,839 --> 00:30:01,980
[SPEAKER_01] jer da su ga opoznali,

688
00:30:01,980 --> 00:30:05,119
[SPEAKER_01] konačnici ne bi činili to pre meni što su činili.

689
00:30:06,880 --> 00:30:08,220
[SPEAKER_01] sve to, znači,

690
00:30:08,220 --> 00:30:10,140
[SPEAKER_01] Patraz jedan često govorio,

691
00:30:10,140 --> 00:30:12,079
[SPEAKER_01] ne pretrat čovjeka su svijet, tijelo i džavo.

692
00:30:12,079 --> 00:30:13,319
[SPEAKER_01] Svijet koji nas vuče se,

693
00:30:13,319 --> 00:30:15,539
[SPEAKER_01] svijet koji ima svoje propagande.

694
00:30:15,539 --> 00:30:18,180
[SPEAKER_01] Onda tu je tijelo koje je puno požude,

695
00:30:18,180 --> 00:30:19,579
[SPEAKER_01] a onda tu je džavo

696
00:30:19,579 --> 00:30:21,640
[SPEAKER_01] koji te vabi

697
00:30:21,640 --> 00:30:22,839
[SPEAKER_01] kroz različite,

698
00:30:22,839 --> 00:30:24,599
[SPEAKER_01] evo, astrologija, horoskop,

699
00:30:24,599 --> 00:30:25,940
[SPEAKER_01] fidovnjaci, hođe,

700
00:30:25,940 --> 00:30:27,400
[SPEAKER_01] sve to gdje sam ja

701
00:30:27,400 --> 00:30:30,039
[SPEAKER_01] sa svojim koracijima išla.

702
00:30:30,039 --> 00:30:32,400
[SPEAKER_01] Ali naravno,

703
00:30:32,400 --> 00:30:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] da bi džavo opće došlo do čovjeka,

704
00:30:35,000 --> 00:30:36,880
[SPEAKER_01] djelovao kroz čovjeka,

705
00:30:36,880 --> 00:30:38,599
[SPEAKER_01] potreba da čovjek bude ranjen.

706
00:30:38,599 --> 00:30:40,019
[SPEAKER_01] Jer on kroz ranu ulazi.

707
00:30:40,019 --> 00:30:42,240
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam prvenstvo bila ranjena

708
00:30:42,240 --> 00:30:43,940
[SPEAKER_01] kad me prvi put moja majka ostavila.

709
00:30:43,940 --> 00:30:46,019
[SPEAKER_01] Bila sam malena djevojčica

710
00:30:46,019 --> 00:30:47,400
[SPEAKER_01] koja je mama bila sve.

711
00:30:47,400 --> 00:30:49,640
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam znači sve imala uzor u svojom majci

712
00:30:49,640 --> 00:30:51,839
[SPEAKER_01] i kasnije kad se ona me ni vratila u život

713
00:30:51,839 --> 00:30:54,559
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam mu na jedan nezrav način kupovala.

714
00:30:54,559 --> 00:30:57,059
[SPEAKER_01] Poklonima, kupovala sam je pažnjom.

715
00:30:57,059 --> 00:30:59,339
[SPEAKER_01] Kupovala sam je time

716
00:30:59,339 --> 00:31:00,759
[SPEAKER_01] da joj ne iznosim neke stvari,

717
00:31:00,759 --> 00:31:02,640
[SPEAKER_01] da ona ne bude povrijeđena time.

718
00:31:02,640 --> 00:31:04,900
[SPEAKER_01] Samo da bi imala svoju majku blizu.

719
00:31:04,900 --> 00:31:06,099
[SPEAKER_01] A to je ono što danas

720
00:31:06,099 --> 00:31:07,160
[SPEAKER_01] mnogo djeca čine.

721
00:31:07,160 --> 00:31:09,240
[SPEAKER_01] Žele privući pažnju roditelja,

722
00:31:09,240 --> 00:31:10,819
[SPEAKER_01] žele kupiti svoje roditele,

723
00:31:10,819 --> 00:31:12,940
[SPEAKER_01] njihovu pažnju, njihovu ljubav,

724
00:31:12,940 --> 00:31:15,059
[SPEAKER_01] a pritom sakreti

725
00:31:15,059 --> 00:31:16,480
[SPEAKER_01] onu stvarnost

726
00:31:16,480 --> 00:31:18,140
[SPEAKER_01] u kojem se oni zaista nalaze.

727
00:31:18,839 --> 00:31:20,980
[SPEAKER_00] Zapravo spomenula sam malo prije ovo

728
00:31:20,980 --> 00:31:23,619
[SPEAKER_00] jer više puta navodiš

729
00:31:23,619 --> 00:31:24,880
[SPEAKER_00] i čitanje horoskopa

730
00:31:24,880 --> 00:31:26,480
[SPEAKER_00] i odlazak kod vidovnjakinje.

731
00:31:26,480 --> 00:31:28,279
[SPEAKER_00] Misli da se to premalo

732
00:31:28,279 --> 00:31:30,299
[SPEAKER_00] naglašava koliko je to

733
00:31:30,299 --> 00:31:31,180
[SPEAKER_00] izvor

734
00:31:31,180 --> 00:31:34,460
[SPEAKER_00] izvor zla zapravo,

735
00:31:34,460 --> 00:31:35,500
[SPEAKER_00] ali možemo reći.

736
00:31:35,500 --> 00:31:38,039
[SPEAKER_00] A možemo pročitati tu

737
00:31:38,039 --> 00:31:39,519
[SPEAKER_00] svakodnevnim časopisima,

738
00:31:39,519 --> 00:31:41,900
[SPEAKER_00] svaki dan na televiziji.

739
00:31:42,420 --> 00:31:43,880
[SPEAKER_00] ti možeš posvjedočiti da je to

740
00:31:43,880 --> 00:31:45,799
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo nije mala šala.

741
00:31:45,799 --> 00:31:46,720
[SPEAKER_01] Nije mala šala.

742
00:31:46,720 --> 00:31:47,200
[SPEAKER_01] Uostalom,

743
00:31:47,200 --> 00:31:48,519
[SPEAKER_01] to je otac laži.

744
00:31:48,519 --> 00:31:51,220
[SPEAKER_01] I šta otac laži ti nudi u horoskopu?

745
00:31:51,220 --> 00:31:52,819
[SPEAKER_01] Da otkriješ kako će ti biti ljubav?

746
00:31:52,819 --> 00:31:53,400
[SPEAKER_01] A koja je ljubav?

747
00:31:53,400 --> 00:31:54,119
[SPEAKER_01] Boga je ljubav.

748
00:31:54,119 --> 00:31:56,180
[SPEAKER_01] Otkrivati zdravlja.

749
00:31:56,180 --> 00:31:57,640
[SPEAKER_01] Što ti vredi zdravo tijelo

750
00:31:57,640 --> 00:31:59,339
[SPEAKER_01] ako ti je zluh slab

751
00:31:59,339 --> 00:32:00,440
[SPEAKER_01] ili duh zarobljen.

752
00:32:00,440 --> 00:32:01,980
[SPEAKER_01] Konačno si nuditi

753
00:32:01,980 --> 00:32:03,400
[SPEAKER_01] tu jednu lažnu

754
00:32:03,400 --> 00:32:05,720
[SPEAKER_01] lažnu nadu

755
00:32:05,720 --> 00:32:08,160
[SPEAKER_01] i prikazanje novac,

756
00:32:08,160 --> 00:32:09,099
[SPEAKER_01] posao.

757
00:32:09,099 --> 00:32:10,359
[SPEAKER_01] Bože,

758
00:32:10,359 --> 00:32:11,799
[SPEAKER_01] ako si ti meni rekao

759
00:32:11,799 --> 00:32:13,180
[SPEAKER_01] da se ne brinem tijeskobno,

760
00:32:13,180 --> 00:32:14,559
[SPEAKER_01] hraniš ptice na grani,

761
00:32:14,559 --> 00:32:15,900
[SPEAKER_01] polsko cijeće oblačeć,

762
00:32:15,900 --> 00:32:17,559
[SPEAKER_01] zašto da se brinem tijeskobno,

763
00:32:17,559 --> 00:32:18,799
[SPEAKER_01] to će meni zloduh

764
00:32:18,799 --> 00:32:20,440
[SPEAKER_01] prorokovati

765
00:32:20,440 --> 00:32:21,980
[SPEAKER_01] na lažan način

766
00:32:21,980 --> 00:32:23,339
[SPEAKER_01] da pročitam

767
00:32:23,339 --> 00:32:25,559
[SPEAKER_01] oću li ja ima sljedeći mjesec novaca ili ne.

768
00:32:25,559 --> 00:32:25,980
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim,

769
00:32:26,559 --> 00:32:28,660
[SPEAKER_01] pa ako nam je svaka vlasna glavi zbrana,

770
00:32:28,660 --> 00:32:30,740
[SPEAKER_01] nijedna neopada bez očeva znanja,

771
00:32:30,740 --> 00:32:32,359
[SPEAKER_01] pa neće joj vjerojat tamo

772
00:32:32,359 --> 00:32:33,559
[SPEAKER_01] jednom horoskopu.

773
00:32:33,559 --> 00:32:35,779
[SPEAKER_01] Ja vjerujem živo me Bogu,

774
00:32:35,779 --> 00:32:36,920
[SPEAKER_01] a se njegovo dijete.

775
00:32:36,920 --> 00:32:38,299
[SPEAKER_01] A što je njegova volja?

776
00:32:38,299 --> 00:32:39,539
[SPEAKER_01] Da život imamo.

777
00:32:39,539 --> 00:32:40,400
[SPEAKER_01] A kako?

778
00:32:40,400 --> 00:32:41,859
[SPEAKER_01] Da mu budemo vjerni,

779
00:32:41,859 --> 00:32:42,680
[SPEAKER_01] da ga slijedimo,

780
00:32:42,680 --> 00:32:44,460
[SPEAKER_01] da vršimo njegove zapovjedi,

781
00:32:44,460 --> 00:32:45,960
[SPEAKER_01] a iznad svega da ga ljubimo,

782
00:32:45,960 --> 00:32:47,480
[SPEAKER_01] njega i bližnjega

783
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:48,480
[SPEAKER_01] ko samoga sebe.

784
00:32:48,480 --> 00:32:52,480
[SPEAKER_00] Da, mislim da tu ono manjak povjerenja.

785
00:32:52,480 --> 00:32:53,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ja znam po sebi, evo,

786
00:32:53,640 --> 00:32:55,859
[SPEAKER_00] trudim se sve više,

787
00:32:56,480 --> 00:33:00,480
[SPEAKER_00] puštati tu kontrolu.

788
00:33:00,480 --> 00:33:03,019
[SPEAKER_00] Mi ljudi bismo htjeli imati neku kontrolu,

789
00:33:03,019 --> 00:33:03,839
[SPEAKER_00] nekakvu

790
00:33:03,839 --> 00:33:06,759
[SPEAKER_00] potpisanu,

791
00:33:06,759 --> 00:33:09,140
[SPEAKER_00] ono, potpisano što će se dogoditi.

792
00:33:09,140 --> 00:33:10,900
[SPEAKER_00] Čisto da mi sebe zaštitimo,

793
00:33:10,900 --> 00:33:12,299
[SPEAKER_00] potencijalnih nekih,

794
00:33:12,299 --> 00:33:15,200
[SPEAKER_00] možda, povrijeđenosti i tako dalje.

795
00:33:15,279 --> 00:33:16,420
[SPEAKER_00] I onda to povjerenje,

796
00:33:16,420 --> 00:33:18,720
[SPEAKER_00] da ne moram znati,

797
00:33:18,720 --> 00:33:20,579
[SPEAKER_00] ne trebam znati što me čeka sutra,

798
00:33:20,579 --> 00:33:22,099
[SPEAKER_00] ali nama ljudima,

799
00:33:22,099 --> 00:33:22,819
[SPEAKER_00] evo ja prvo...

800
00:33:22,819 --> 00:33:24,039
[SPEAKER_00] Svi smo radoznali.

801
00:33:24,039 --> 00:33:25,279
[SPEAKER_00] Da, svi smo radoznali

802
00:33:25,279 --> 00:33:27,740
[SPEAKER_00] i želimo kontrolirati situaciju.

803
00:33:27,819 --> 00:33:29,839
[SPEAKER_01] E, ali to ti sve zajedno,

804
00:33:29,839 --> 00:33:30,700
[SPEAKER_01] radoznalost,

805
00:33:30,700 --> 00:33:31,880
[SPEAKER_01] kontrola

806
00:33:31,880 --> 00:33:33,319
[SPEAKER_01] i nestrpljivost.

807
00:33:33,319 --> 00:33:33,640
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

808
00:33:33,700 --> 00:33:34,940
[SPEAKER_01] A to sve voditi jedno s drugim.

809
00:33:34,940 --> 00:33:36,660
[SPEAKER_01] Ljudi često su nestrpljivi,

810
00:33:36,660 --> 00:33:38,440
[SPEAKER_01] radoznali što će biti

811
00:33:38,440 --> 00:33:40,240
[SPEAKER_01] i htjeli bi imati sve pod kontrolom.

812
00:33:40,240 --> 00:33:41,740
[SPEAKER_01] To su sve sestrice.

813
00:33:41,740 --> 00:33:44,460
[SPEAKER_01] Isti kruk koji veže jedan s drugim.

814
00:33:44,460 --> 00:33:46,359
[SPEAKER_01] Zato treba se toga osloboditi

815
00:33:46,359 --> 00:33:48,700
[SPEAKER_01] i samo tražiti Bože kraljestvo

816
00:33:48,700 --> 00:33:49,579
[SPEAKER_01] i pravdu u njegovu.

817
00:33:49,579 --> 00:33:50,539
[SPEAKER_01] I to svakodnevno.

818
00:33:50,539 --> 00:33:51,779
[SPEAKER_01] Umirati sebe,

819
00:33:51,779 --> 00:33:53,200
[SPEAKER_01] derovati se za njega

820
00:33:53,200 --> 00:33:55,279
[SPEAKER_01] i u konačnosti ljubiti bližnjega.

821
00:33:55,279 --> 00:33:56,240
[SPEAKER_01] Jel'i...

822
00:33:56,240 --> 00:33:57,240
[SPEAKER_01] Gdje je moja plaća?

823
00:33:57,240 --> 00:33:58,299
[SPEAKER_01] Tu, među bližnjima.

824
00:33:58,299 --> 00:33:59,119
[SPEAKER_01] Gdje je među onima

825
00:33:59,119 --> 00:34:00,279
[SPEAKER_01] i koji mene proganjaju,

826
00:34:00,279 --> 00:34:01,819
[SPEAKER_01] koji mene razumiju,

827
00:34:01,819 --> 00:34:03,819
[SPEAKER_01] koji me kleveću,

828
00:34:03,819 --> 00:34:05,059
[SPEAKER_01] koji me ismijavanju.

829
00:34:05,059 --> 00:34:05,539
[SPEAKER_01] Pa Bože,

830
00:34:05,539 --> 00:34:08,440
[SPEAKER_01] ja im neću uzvraćati njihov način.

831
00:34:08,440 --> 00:34:09,980
[SPEAKER_01] Ne zašto što možda oni,

832
00:34:09,980 --> 00:34:11,460
[SPEAKER_01] možda njegi njeni ne ubodu.

833
00:34:11,460 --> 00:34:14,340
[SPEAKER_01] Nego zato što si me ti pozvao

834
00:34:14,340 --> 00:34:15,239
[SPEAKER_01] na ljubav.

835
00:34:15,239 --> 00:34:17,320
[SPEAKER_01] I ako sam ja shvatila

836
00:34:17,320 --> 00:34:18,500
[SPEAKER_01] Boži poziv,

837
00:34:18,500 --> 00:34:19,780
[SPEAKER_01] šta je ljubav?

838
00:34:19,780 --> 00:34:22,219
[SPEAKER_01] Onda znam da neću uzvraćati mirom

839
00:34:22,219 --> 00:34:23,579
[SPEAKER_01] koji oni me mjere

840
00:34:23,579 --> 00:34:25,659
[SPEAKER_01] ili sudom koji me oni sude.

841
00:34:25,659 --> 00:34:27,739
[SPEAKER_00] Jel'i se nekad osjetiš usamljena

842
00:34:27,739 --> 00:34:30,360
[SPEAKER_00] na toj razini duhovnosti?

843
00:34:30,360 --> 00:34:31,519
[SPEAKER_00] Jel' ti teško pronaći

844
00:34:31,519 --> 00:34:33,519
[SPEAKER_00] prijateljice koje te razumiju?

845
00:34:33,519 --> 00:34:36,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ja Bogu hvala imam i prijateljice.

846
00:34:36,199 --> 00:34:37,619
[SPEAKER_01] Tu su i moje kume

847
00:34:37,619 --> 00:34:39,760
[SPEAKER_01] i kuma kata

848
00:34:39,760 --> 00:34:41,340
[SPEAKER_01] koja mi je duhovna majka,

849
00:34:41,340 --> 00:34:42,780
[SPEAKER_01] tu časna sestra Matija Pavić,

850
00:34:42,780 --> 00:34:43,420
[SPEAKER_01] poglavarica,

851
00:34:43,420 --> 00:34:45,099
[SPEAKER_01] krenateljica Krvi Kristovi,

852
00:34:45,099 --> 00:34:45,780
[SPEAKER_01] svećenici,

853
00:34:45,780 --> 00:34:47,539
[SPEAKER_01] moji duhovni oci koji me prate,

854
00:34:47,539 --> 00:34:48,199
[SPEAKER_01] moj duhovnik,

855
00:34:48,199 --> 00:34:48,980
[SPEAKER_01] fraj Ivan Matić.

856
00:34:48,980 --> 00:34:51,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ja zaista imam veliku milost,

857
00:34:51,760 --> 00:34:53,400
[SPEAKER_01] moje srce ima veliku milost

858
00:34:53,400 --> 00:34:55,420
[SPEAKER_01] da imam predivne ljude

859
00:34:55,420 --> 00:34:56,800
[SPEAKER_01] u mom životu,

860
00:34:56,800 --> 00:34:57,539
[SPEAKER_01] ne oko mene,

861
00:34:57,539 --> 00:34:59,079
[SPEAKER_01] nego u mome životu,

862
00:34:59,079 --> 00:35:00,099
[SPEAKER_01] u mome srcu,

863
00:35:00,099 --> 00:35:01,260
[SPEAKER_01] savjetima,

864
00:35:01,260 --> 00:35:01,940
[SPEAKER_01] ljubavlju,

865
00:35:01,940 --> 00:35:02,820
[SPEAKER_01] brigom,

866
00:35:02,820 --> 00:35:04,019
[SPEAKER_01] milosrđem,

867
00:35:04,019 --> 00:35:05,360
[SPEAKER_01] opomenom,

868
00:35:05,360 --> 00:35:06,280
[SPEAKER_01] ukorom,

869
00:35:06,280 --> 00:35:08,039
[SPEAKER_01] tješenjem,

870
00:35:08,039 --> 00:35:09,300
[SPEAKER_01] utjehom i svemu.

871
00:35:09,300 --> 00:35:10,940
[SPEAKER_01] Zaista i to je veliki dar

872
00:35:10,940 --> 00:35:12,820
[SPEAKER_01] i na tobe ne prostano zahvalju.

873
00:35:14,119 --> 00:35:18,699
[SPEAKER_00] Jel ti nekad bude ono osjećaj kao da želiš spasiti neke ljude iz svoje prošlosti?

874
00:35:18,699 --> 00:35:19,179
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno.

875
00:35:19,179 --> 00:35:21,219
[SPEAKER_00] Prije nego što nastavimo s razgovorom,

876
00:35:21,219 --> 00:35:25,380
[SPEAKER_00] samo mali podsjetnik da današnju epizodu ponosno sponsorira like,

877
00:35:25,380 --> 00:35:28,579
[SPEAKER_00] hrvatski brand personaliziranog predivnog nakita.

878
00:35:28,579 --> 00:35:30,860
[SPEAKER_00] Njihovi komadi nisu samo ukrasne,

879
00:35:30,860 --> 00:35:36,039
[SPEAKER_00] nego dolaze sa mirisnim medaljonima koji subtilno odpuštaju parfem ili eterično ulje kroz dan.

880
00:35:36,699 --> 00:35:38,980
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki komad možeš personalizirati gravurom,

881
00:35:38,980 --> 00:35:42,559
[SPEAKER_00] odabrati motiv i boju pozlate,

882
00:35:42,559 --> 00:35:46,460
[SPEAKER_00] tako da je like savršen kao pokloni ili mala uspomena za sebe.

883
00:35:46,460 --> 00:35:49,579
[SPEAKER_00] Izrađeni su od kvalitetnih hipoalergenih materijala,

884
00:35:49,579 --> 00:35:51,219
[SPEAKER_00] pa su ugodni za nositi svaki dan.

885
00:35:51,219 --> 00:35:53,179
[SPEAKER_00] Ako želiš vidjeti sve uživo,

886
00:35:53,179 --> 00:35:56,199
[SPEAKER_00] posjeti njihov predivni showroom u Zagrebu,

887
00:35:56,199 --> 00:35:59,699
[SPEAKER_00] a naravno da sve možeš vidjeti i na njihovoj web trgovini.

888
00:35:59,699 --> 00:36:02,059
[SPEAKER_00] A sedajmo nazad na razgovor.

889
00:36:02,059 --> 00:36:05,500
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno, problemstveno ljudi iz moje obitelji

890
00:36:05,500 --> 00:36:10,380
[SPEAKER_01] i bilo mi teško i stvarno sad bih ja cupkala za rukav.

891
00:36:10,380 --> 00:36:12,559
[SPEAKER_01] Ajde, dođi, dođi na izvor, dođi Isusu.

892
00:36:12,559 --> 00:36:15,139
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to je to što je Boga silan i nasilan.

893
00:36:15,139 --> 00:36:18,159
[SPEAKER_01] Nikog ne možemo na silu dovodi gospodinu, nikog.

894
00:36:18,159 --> 00:36:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Možemo mu posvjedočiti,

895
00:36:20,000 --> 00:36:23,320
[SPEAKER_01] a na osobi da će mu biti otvoreno srce

896
00:36:23,320 --> 00:36:25,539
[SPEAKER_01] i oće li ona primiti to svjedočanstvo.

897
00:36:25,539 --> 00:36:27,340
[SPEAKER_01] I u redu je ako ne primi,

898
00:36:27,340 --> 00:36:29,800
[SPEAKER_01] ako je još zatvorena iz nekih svojih rana,

899
00:36:29,800 --> 00:36:31,360
[SPEAKER_01] pobuna, zarobljenosti.

900
00:36:31,360 --> 00:36:33,380
[SPEAKER_01] Sve je to normalno, sve je to u redu.

901
00:36:33,380 --> 00:36:36,280
[SPEAKER_01] Ne treba gledati, aha, ako neko nije otvoren za svjedočanstvo,

902
00:36:36,280 --> 00:36:38,239
[SPEAKER_01] neko nije otvoren evo za osobu koja

903
00:36:38,239 --> 00:36:40,199
[SPEAKER_01] se to prvobitno obratila.

904
00:36:40,199 --> 00:36:42,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ja kažem, zato je obročenje proces koji traje cijeli život.

905
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:44,280
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, sve je to u redu.

906
00:36:44,280 --> 00:36:46,559
[SPEAKER_01] To prihvaćanje u redu, prihvaćam te, sestro.

907
00:36:46,559 --> 00:36:48,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ti ne razumiješ moj put,

908
00:36:48,579 --> 00:36:50,340
[SPEAKER_01] ne razumiješ dar vjere

909
00:36:50,340 --> 00:36:52,699
[SPEAKER_01] koju se moj srce trudi živjet,

910
00:36:52,699 --> 00:36:54,639
[SPEAKER_01] ne razumiješ dar poziva,

911
00:36:54,639 --> 00:36:55,599
[SPEAKER_01] svjedočanstva,

912
00:36:56,000 --> 00:36:57,360
[SPEAKER_01] kojima se izlažem.

913
00:36:57,360 --> 00:36:58,159
[SPEAKER_01] I to je u redu.

914
00:36:58,159 --> 00:36:59,039
[SPEAKER_01] To je u redu.

915
00:36:59,039 --> 00:37:02,679
[SPEAKER_01] Ali nekako, uvijek pazim da se ne diram moja obitelj.

916
00:37:02,679 --> 00:37:04,920
[SPEAKER_01] Eto, onda postanem ona lavica.

917
00:37:04,920 --> 00:37:06,019
[SPEAKER_01] Stop, dosta je.

918
00:37:06,019 --> 00:37:08,079
[SPEAKER_01] Na mog muža, djecu, to ne dam.

919
00:37:08,079 --> 00:37:09,760
[SPEAKER_01] To sam zaista, tu sam borbena.

920
00:37:09,760 --> 00:37:11,880
[SPEAKER_01] I tu mi nekak, onda moj muž mora malo,

921
00:37:11,880 --> 00:37:13,260
[SPEAKER_01] saj, smiri se, smiri se.

922
00:37:13,260 --> 00:37:16,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ali na to, kad neko dirne u moju djecu,

923
00:37:16,019 --> 00:37:17,599
[SPEAKER_01] to znam odgovoriti.

924
00:37:17,599 --> 00:37:19,300
[SPEAKER_01] Ali opet, tu se nekako mrtim.

925
00:37:19,300 --> 00:37:21,619
[SPEAKER_01] Bože, umrti me u sakramentima.

926
00:37:21,619 --> 00:37:22,400
[SPEAKER_01] Da zaista, onda,

927
00:37:22,400 --> 00:37:25,179
[SPEAKER_01] mislim, ne da ne uzrećem ono sad za zlo

928
00:37:25,179 --> 00:37:27,380
[SPEAKER_01] ili da nekom uđelazim u rasprave,

929
00:37:27,380 --> 00:37:31,619
[SPEAKER_01] ali znam i te kako oštro uđu u obranu svoje obitelje.

930
00:37:31,619 --> 00:37:34,300
[SPEAKER_00] Čula sam da se zahvaljuješ novinarima

931
00:37:34,300 --> 00:37:36,340
[SPEAKER_00] jer nisu na promociji knjige Djecu slikali.

932
00:37:36,340 --> 00:37:38,519
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, to je trebalo unaprijed dogovoriti.

933
00:37:38,519 --> 00:37:40,019
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ne, ja sam to rekla.

934
00:37:40,019 --> 00:37:43,320
[SPEAKER_01] To biti znaju da ja svoju djecu ne slikam.

935
00:37:43,320 --> 00:37:45,940
[SPEAKER_01] Ne stavljam ih po društvenim mrežama.

936
00:37:46,019 --> 00:37:49,760
[SPEAKER_01] i to je, to sam dobila poziv u srcu od mojeg gospodina.

937
00:37:49,760 --> 00:37:52,639
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno, moj muš je složio tim.

938
00:37:52,639 --> 00:37:56,219
[SPEAKER_01] Patr Ivan je to podržao moj duhovnik,

939
00:37:56,219 --> 00:37:57,800
[SPEAKER_01] u ostali mi ostali svećenici.

940
00:37:57,800 --> 00:38:01,159
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, nekomu to može biti jasno,

941
00:38:01,159 --> 00:38:02,380
[SPEAKER_01] nekom može biti nejasno,

942
00:38:02,380 --> 00:38:03,760
[SPEAKER_01] nekom može to blagosloviti,

943
00:38:03,760 --> 00:38:06,019
[SPEAKER_01] nekom to može proganjati i smijavati.

944
00:38:06,019 --> 00:38:08,900
[SPEAKER_01] Ali na meni nije to da ja raspravljam o tome,

945
00:38:08,900 --> 00:38:11,599
[SPEAKER_01] niti da uopće gledam koje što rekam.

